/*
 * Empty placeholder DTBO.
 *
 * begonia/begoniain no longer split the SoC dtb out as a DTBO overlay
 * (see "arm64: dts: mediatek: Merge base SoC DTB into begonia"), so
 * there are no real overlay fragments to package. The dtbo partition
 * on this device still needs a validly-formed (MTK cert-signed) image
 * though, and mkdtboimg refuses to build a zero-entry table. Keep this
 * no-op fragment around purely so drvgen has one real entry to package.
 */

/dts-v1/;
/plugin/;

